  dwmstatus
=============

 Status bar utility for dwm written in Go with XCB that shows: date,
load, memory, I/O and network statistics.

 It features sending local/remote notifications and showing stats of
another machine.


 Usage
-------

See `dwmstatus -h' and `main.go'.


